[[File:Commander Connad chathead.png|left]]
'''Commander Connad''' is a barbarian located on the main floor of the [[Barbarian Outpost]]. He runs the [[Barbarian Assault Reward Shop]] for the [[Barbarian Assault]] [[minigame]]: players who have earned [[honour points]] while playing the [[minigame]] can talk to him to access the [[Barbarian Assault/Rewards|Reward Shop]]. There, players can spend points on levelling up their roles, buying penance gear, or gambling for items. Players can also talk to him to get their wave in the minigame reset to 1, or use penance gear on him to receive a point refund equal to 80% of the purchase price. he will not refund [[(broken)]] items, however he will refund [[(l)|locked]] items, consuming the [[trouver parchment]] in the process, so it is recommended to unlock before refuding

